    "en": {
      "name": "Power Patron Shadows of the End Times",
      "effect": "Special Summon 1 \"Power Patron\" monster from your hand, face-up Extra Deck, or GY, then you can apply any of the following effects, in sequence, based on the number of different card types (Fusion, Synchro, Xyz) you control.\n\u25cf 1+: Banish (face-down) the top 3 cards of your opponent's Deck.\n\u25cf 2+: Banish (face-down) 1 card your opponent controls.\n\u25cf 3: Banish (face-down) 1 random card from your opponent's hand.\nYou can only activate 1 \"Power Patron Shadows of the End Times\" per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
